data.description: Great location! Only 6 min from popular Olde Town Arvada! Located on a quiet cul-de-sac street with no neighbors behind you.  Walking distance to the local elementary school. Partially remodeled with new laminated, anti-scratch wood flooring throughout the property. Newly remodeled and updated bathrooms. The 3 bedrooms, new carpet will be installed before closing and some paint to make it your own. Bright and open floor plan, flooded with natural light!  Don't miss out on this opportunity. New furnace will be installed, and the seller is offering a home warranty. Seller had done sewer scope inspection available upon request.
